# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Agentic RAG System — Environment Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# Never commit real API keys to version control.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Groq API key (required).
# Get yours at: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Tavily API key for web search augmentation.
# Get yours at: https://app.tavily.com/home
TAVILY_API_KEY=your_tavily_api_key_here

# ── Authentication ────────────────────────────────────
# Secret key for signing JWT tokens. Generate with:
#   python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(64))"
JWT_SECRET=CHANGE_ME_generate_a_real_secret_here

# ── Storage Paths ─────────────────────────────────────
# Path where ChromaDB persists its vector store.
CHROMA_DB_PATH=./chroma_data

# Path to the SQLite database file for metadata/traces.
SQLITE_DB_PATH=./agentic_rag.db

# ── Model Configuration ──────────────────────────────
# HuggingFace embedding model used for vector embeddings.
EMBEDDING_MODEL=all-MiniLM-L6-v2

# Cross-encoder model used for reranking retrieved chunks.
RERANKER_MODEL=cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2

# ── Feature Toggles ──────────────────────────────────
ENABLE_WEB_SEARCH=true
ENABLE_LLM_FALLBACK=true

# ── Retry Limits ──────────────────────────────────────
MAX_RETRIEVAL_RETRIES=3
MAX_GENERATION_RETRIES=2

# ── Thresholds ────────────────────────────────────────
HALLUCINATION_THRESHOLD=0.2
ROUTING_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD=0.7

# ── Retrieval Settings ────────────────────────────────
TOP_K_RETRIEVAL=20
TOP_K_FINAL=5

# ── Frontend URL ──────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated list of allowed frontend origins for CORS.
FRONTEND_URLS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000

ANONYMIZED_TELEMETRY=False

# ── Frontend Specific (Vite) ──────────────────────────
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080/api
